                <p style="font-size:10pt;font-family:SansSerif;color:#4b4b4b;padding:2px;text-align:justify;margin: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/>During the validity of the aforesaid charge on a Unit, all the cheques/payments towards consideration as well as pass through amounts relating to the Unit shall be drawn only in the name of the aforesaid Account /Beneficiary by the Allottees. Payments made in any other account / in favour of any other beneficiary will be null and void, unless specifically agreed otherwise in writing by Financer and the Promoters.<br/></p>
